(Intercept)       0.285617 0.1291054  0.6318641
difficultyeasy    2.359897 1.2971580  4.2933192
statusdominant    1.950708 0.7743205  4.9143237
statussubordinate 4.304281 1.4106406 13.1336310
```
:::
