How many participants in each condition? We know from the description there should be 10 in each, but lets check!

::: {.cell layout-align="center"}

```{.r .cell-code}
mmd |> 
  group_by(condition) |>
  summarise(
    n_ppt = n_distinct(ppt)
  )
